Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy made it to Marineford to rescue \Nhis brother, Ace who will be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He and the Whitebeards finally got over the \Ncling walls to make it to the scaffold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an all-out battle between the Navy and  \Nthe Whitebeards continues at the Oris Plaza,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy runs toward Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you can't win out against the \Nonslaught of time, Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was afraid of the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have an unguarded moment, \Nyou will lose the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't look away like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I be the last voice \Nyou hear before you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd be able to do all I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be happy to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me fight, Ivan-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't fight now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if I can't rescue Ace, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather take my own life afterwards!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have the strength to fight for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To Live Up to a Promise! \NLuffy and Coby Collide!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So slow! What's taking them so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought two executioners as replacements!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Finally! Hurry and get ready!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw boy, once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you better keep in mind that the next time \Nyou drop, you won't be able to bounce back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Energy Hormone is just fooling your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't repairing any of the damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't fall again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Another foolhardy statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to execute Ace again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, my words can't change Straw \Nboy's mind under these circumstances!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do is keep them from beating him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over! I won't let \Nyou pass through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--If you wanna advance...\N--...You gotta beat all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show you the spirit of the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heads up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Wink!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 points! I'll back you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Ivan-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to be the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so if I die fighting for \Nthat, that's fine with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose I can do it, too? \NIf I'm prepared to die for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think... even I could join the Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Catching bad guys is my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been my dream ever since I was little!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't met Luffy-san, I \Ncouldn't have become what I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! In order to \Nlive as a Navy soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to fight to change myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is a battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to commit myself towards killing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a Navy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...admiral someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Oh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm sorry! I got carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing! I wanna crawl in a hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I met you, I became \Nemboldened a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna fight me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, of course you have to \Nbecome such a heavy hitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I can become an admiral?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time we see each other, \Nwe'll be much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And much greater!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They know that it's just a wild dream that \Nmakes me lightheaded at just the thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how can they believe in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's as strong as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless. I have to \Nbecome much much stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Kuma imposters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! What a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boa Hancock. The Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abort attack. Friendly operative.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You guys are on the same side!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the empress, right? \NHow do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! He called my name again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hancock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time he calls me like that, I'm so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hancock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hancock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hancock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move aside, Boa Hancock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to call my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magma brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are off guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a couple more of these \Nand get yourself a good rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things don't always go the way you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course,  Marco the Phoenix regenerates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's your turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Prism Stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Jozu has been beaten, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They even beat our commanders one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're falling apart! \NThe Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You Fish-Man monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, beat Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:32.36,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They think that they can beat me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any help because I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hesitate! He's wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Everybody, follow me!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he call me wounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous! I won't \Ndie from such a small wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die from... such a small...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:19:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow myself to die until...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I see a bright future ahead for my sons!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dotard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are they doing?! Guarding \Nthe back of Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they willing to die with Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't have to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll defend Pops' glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too thoughtful, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Squard,  let's go \Nand fight with Pops, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay the price in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna see the future, \NI'll show you now, Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that I can't \Nstop you for doing it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See it for yourself, Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, was that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conqueror's... Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on! For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:22:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was surprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy unconsciously used the Conqueror's \NHaki and stopped Ace's execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Navy, wary of his \Ndisplay of latent power,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.85,0:23:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,combine their efforts in an \Nattempt to eliminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just then, Iva-san finally \Nreveals his last trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Scaffold at Last! The \NWay to Ace Has Opened!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
